attributes.Long form description: The student opens the GoPro case, grabs the GoPro, and inspects it. The student presses the recording button of the GoPro. The student inspects the GoPro looking for its battery door. The instructor tells the student where the battery door is located and asks him to pull it up. The student pulls the battery door but struggles to open it. The student pulls the battery door harder, unlocks it, and opens it. The student inspects the battery, grabs it from its little strip, and removes it from the battery slot of the GoPro. The student places the battery on the table. The student inspects the battery slot looking for the Sd card and the instructor tells the student how the Sd card looks. The student pushes on the Sd card, detaches it, and removes it from the GoPro. The student holds the Sd card in his left hand and inserts it back into the GoPro. The student pushes on the Sd card and attaches it to the GoPro. The student grabs the battery, inserts it into the battery slot of the GoPro, and closes the battery door. The student briefly inspects the GoPro. The student grabs the mount of the strap from the box and attaches the GoPro to it. The student grabs the lock screw, inserts it into the mount, and screws the GoPro and mount together. The student unscrews the lock screw, removes it, and detaches the GoPro from the mount. The student places the mount and its lock screw inside the GoPro case and closes it. The student opens the bigger case, grabs and moves some documents, and grabs the handheld grip. The student grabs the GoPro, places it on the table again, and opens the GoPro case. The student grabs the GoPro and attaches it to the handheld grip. The student grabs the lock screw, inserts it into the handheld grip, struggles for a moment but finally screws the GoPro and handheld together. The student removes the lock screw from the handheld grip and places it inside the GoPro case. The student detaches the GoPro from the handheld grip and places the handheld grip inside the bigger case.
